Package org.jsonurl.jsonorg Description

A JSON→URL parser and text generator based on Douglas Crockford's original Java implementation of JSON.

The primary entry point for most use cases is JsonUrlParser, which parses JSON→URL text as instances of JSONObject and JSONArray.

JSON→URL text may be generated for instances of JSONObject and JSONArray via JsonUrlStringBuilder.
